					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">4x4 or even 6x6 would probably work, using a reasonably-sized square table.
<br />
<br />(a + b)^2 = a^2 + b^2 + 2*a*b
<br />((a + b)^2 - a^2 - b^2)/2 = a*b</div>

